     ## Summary[0m[2m of Fixes[0m[2m
     
     ###[0m[2m Problem[0m[2m 1[0m[2m: Overs[0m[2melling[0m[2m (Race[0m[2m Condition)[0m[2m
     **Root[0m[2m cause**:[0m[2m The[0m[2m original[0m[2m code[0m[2m had separate[0m[2m `[0m[2mcheck_stock[0m[2m`[0m[2m and `[0m[2mdecrement[0m[2m` operations[0m[2m. Two[0m[2m concurrent requests[0m[2m could both[0m[2m pass[0m[2m the[0m[2m stock check[0m[2m before either[0m[2m decre[0m[2mmented,[0m[2m causing[0m[2m overselling[0m[2m.
     
