     **[0m[2mFix**:[0m[2m Reordered[0m[2m the[0m[2m flow to[0m[2m: reserve[0m[2m inventory →[0m[2m charge →[0m[2m ([0m[2mrelease[0m[2m inventory[0m[2m on[0m[2m failure).[0m[2m Now[0m[2m inventory is[0m[2m reserved BEFORE[0m[2m charging[0m[2m, so[0m[2m if payment[0m[2m fails,[0m[2m the[0m[2m reserved stock[0m[2m is returned[0m[2m.[0m[2m There's[0m[2m no scenario[0m[2m where payment[0m[2m succeeds but[0m[2m the[0m[2m customer[0m[2m gets[0m[2m nothing[0m[2m.
     
     ###[0m[2m Problem[0m[2m 3:[0m[2m Duplicate Charges[0m[2m
     **[0m[2mFix[0m[2m**:[0m[2m Added id[0m[2mempotency[0m[2m to `[0m[2mPaymentGateway[0m[2m.ch[0m[2marge[0m[2m()` by[0m[2m tracking charged[0m[2m `[0m[2morder_id[0m[2m`s in[0m[2m a set[0m[2m with[0m[2m lock[0m[2m protection.[0m[2m The[0m[2m same order[0m[2m_id[0m[2m cannot be[0m[2m charged twice[0m[2m.
     
     ###[0m[2m New[0m[2m Methods Added[0m[2m (pres[0m[2merving public[0m[2m interfaces):[0m[2m
     - `[0m[2mInventory.reserve[0m[2m([0m[2mquantity)`[0m[2m - atom[0m[2mically check[0m[2m and decrement[0m[2m
